[quote=&quot;jcsmcdouall&quot;:30r8ili3]My room description reads &quot;You are in a the hall&quot; or if &quot;You are in prefix...&quot; is disabled then it reads &quot;A the hall&quot;. Is there a way to get rid of the &quot;a&quot;?[/quote:30r8ili3]

I am pretty new to Quest, but I think I can help you. Choose the room in quest -&gt; go to setup tab -&gt; untick the &quot;use default prefix and suffix&quot;

I hope it works for you.
